        What Is a Sustainability Declaration When Selling Property in Queensland?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queensland sellers are required to provide a sustainability declaration to buyers before contracts are signed. Here is what it covers, when it must be provided, and what happens if you get it wrong.
      </p>
    </div>
